note top of Factory
  Factory Pattern: Creates provider
  instances based on specified type.
  Enables runtime provider selection.
end note

note bottom of CommonIF
  Strategy Pattern: Common interfaces
  allow interchangeable cloud providers
  with consistent API across all platforms.
end note

note right of "Authentication Layer"
  Authentication layer handles
  credentials and request signing
  for each cloud provider.
end note

note bottom of "External Cloud APIs"
  Provider implementations connect
  to external cloud APIs through
  HTTP/HTTPS requests.
end note

@enduml
